ter Inc.=E2=80=99s cash flows, anyway=C2=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0it is definitely =
still a part of postmodern financial analysis. In particular, if you have s=
ome crypto project,=C2=A0which almost by definition doesn=E2=80=99t have ca=
