ryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> a thin=
g</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Even as a cold night started to settle outside=
 Tesla=E2=80=98s headquarters here on Saturday, a group of cryptocurrency e=
ntrepreneurs had no plans to leave until Elon Musk, the man they named thei=
r currency after, accepted a 12,000-pound sculpture of a Mr. Musk-headed go=
at riding a rocket.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It is the latest stunt in the cryptocurrency s=
pace, where jokes and memes about digital currencies regularly flood social=
 media. But a 6-ton sculpture as a marketing gimmick isn=E2=80=99t so commo=
n.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The creators of Elon GOAT say the name of thei=
r cryptocurrency was inspired by their respect for Mr. Musk. They and his o=
ther fans think he is the =E2=80=9Cgreatest of all time,=E2=80=9D or a =E2=
=80=9CGOAT.=E2=80=9D They took the admiration literally, spending $600,000 =
to create a sculpture of Mr. Musk=E2=80=99s head, wearing a gold-plated dog=
ecoin necklace on a goat=E2=80=99s body. The rocket can move, pointing to t=
he sky as if it is taking off. Gas lines run through it so that flames can =
shoot out of the back.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">They trucked it to Tesla Inc.=E2=80=99s headqu=
arters, in hopes Mr. Musk would accept the gift. The creators are calling c=
alled the event =E2=80=9CGOATSgiving.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But so far Mr. Musk hasn=E2=80=99t given any i=
ndication he would accept it or whether he knew the sculpture was there. Te=
sla didn=E2=80=99t respond to a request for comment. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Alec Wolvert, an Elon GOAT co-founder and chie=
f marketing officer, said they were planning on camping out on a piece of p=
ublic land off a toll road that overlooks the headquarters until Mr. Musk a=
ccepted the sculpture.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CWe=E2=80=99re gonna stay here as long=
 as possible,=E2=80=9D Mr. Wolvert said. =E2=80=9CI even heard some people =
say they were going to strap themselves to it.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The idea of the sculpture came together last y=
ear. =E2=80=9CIt was an evening joke that kind of just came to fruition,=E2=
=80=9D said Ashley Sansalone, an Elon GOAT co-founder. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CElon tweeting us would legitimize the=
 token,=E2=80=9D said Mr. Sansalone, 40 years old.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Would it? In what sense? There are pictures.</=
